{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "a7dc59a9-1c15-47d6-87e1-0fd4f8c0bfa5", "type": 201, "content": {"expand_field": [{"id": "d2c24d1a-2a96-4f6e-936d-8d1a951fd3b3", "type": "array", "value": ["①朝三暮四：引申为反复无常。②痴儿：指贪财恋色的富而痴之人。荣枯：指事物的兴衰，情理的得失。事：道理。③家私：家财。④花枝：指女色。⑤壮起荒淫志：生出荒淫的心思。⑥锭：金银的量词。招状纸：罪犯招供的文书。", "对两首词理解和分析不恰当的一项是（　　）"], "key": "注释"}], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a7dc59a9-1c15-47d6-87e1-0fd4f8c0bfa5@2.pkg/1772602203188/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602203618", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a7dc59a9-1c15-47d6-87e1-0fd4f8c0bfa5@2.pkg/1772602203188/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602203618"}, "identifier": "a7dc59a9-1c15-47d6-87e1-0fd4f8c0bfa5", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B．有误，&ldquo;意踌躇&rdquo;写出了作者看到长安从繁盛到荒凉的沧桑巨变，不由感慨横生的样子。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阅读下面两首词，完成下列题目。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>山坡羊•潼关怀古</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;张养浩（元）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>峰峦如聚，波涛如怒，山河表里潼关路。望西都，意踌躇。伤心秦汉经行处，宫阙万间都做了土。兴，百姓苦；亡，百姓苦！</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>山坡羊•冬日写怀</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 乔吉（元）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>朝三暮四</span><span><sup>①</sup></span><span>，昨非今是，痴儿不解荣枯事</span><span><sup>②</sup></span><span>。攒家私</span><span><sup>③</sup></span><span>，宠花枝</span><span><sup>④</sup></span><span>，黄金壮起荒淫志</span><span><sup>⑤</sup></span><span>。千百锭买张招状纸</span><span><sup>⑥</sup></span><span>。身，已至此；心，犹未死。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>​</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>​关于两首诗的分析，错误的是哪一项</span></p>\n</div>\n", "label": "", "title": "阅读下面两首词，完成下列题目。山坡羊•潼关怀古                                  张养浩（元）峰峦如聚，波涛如怒，山河表里潼关路。望西都，意踌躇。伤心秦汉经行处，宫阙万间都做了土。兴，百姓苦；亡，百姓苦！山坡羊•冬日写怀                                 乔吉（元）朝三暮四①，昨非今是，痴儿不解荣枯事②。攒家私③，宠花枝④，黄金壮起荒淫", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a7dc59a9-1c15-47d6-87e1-0fd4f8c0bfa5@2.pkg/item.json?v=1748320684916", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>两首元曲都采用了&ldquo;山坡羊&rdquo;这一曲牌名，具有相同的音乐节奏和韵律特点。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>张曲中</span><span>&ldquo;意踌躇&rdquo;一词表达了作者看到长安衰败的景象而内心犹豫不决的状态。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>乔曲通过讽刺和批判的手法，揭露了某些人追求财富和享乐而迷失自我的社会现象。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>两首元曲在主题上有异曲同工之妙，张曲关注历史兴衰和百姓疾苦，乔曲</span><span>借冬日写怀来批判社会现象。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阅读下面两首词，完成下列题目。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>山坡羊•潼关怀古</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;张养浩（元）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>峰峦如聚，波涛如怒，山河表里潼关路。望西都，意踌躇。伤心秦汉经行处，宫阙万间都做了土。兴，百姓苦；亡，百姓苦！</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>山坡羊•冬日写怀</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 乔吉（元）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>朝三暮四</span><span><sup>①</sup></span><span>，昨非今是，痴儿不解荣枯事</span><span><sup>②</sup></span><span>。攒家私</span><span><sup>③</sup></span><span>，宠花枝</span><span><sup>④</sup></span><span>，黄金壮起荒淫志</span><span><sup>⑤</sup></span><span>。千百锭买张招状纸</span><span><sup>⑥</sup></span><span>。身，已至此；心，犹未死。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>​</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>​关于两首诗的分析，错误的是哪一项</span></p>\n</div>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_nce